title: Awdis Printed Hoodie
description:
The AWDis college hoodie is comfortable and high-quality, ideal for schools, sports teams, promotional clothing and more. With a double fabric hood, self-coloured cords, and ribbed cuffs, it has a premium, retail feel like our many other AWDis hoodies.

This personalised hoodie also has a simple tear-off label, which allows the garment to be easily rebranded. This is ideal for resellers looking to create their own brand.

With many customisation options available for colour and sizing, you can create your hoodie to your exact needs. This hoodie can be personalised with your own logo or design, with several options available for printing and embroidery. So, choose the AWDis college hoodie as the ideal choice for you and your group.

Features:

  • Huge range of colours makes this a really versatile choice
  • Durable and well-designed for a premium retail feel
  • Contains a tear-out label for easy re-branding
  • Double fabric hood with self-coloured cords
  • Front kangaroo pouch pocket
  • Ribbed cuffs and hem
  • Twin needle stitching detailing provides added strength and durability
  • Soft, cotton-faced fabric creates an ideal printing surface
  • Worldwide Responsible Accredited Production (WRAP) certified production

This personalised hoodie also has a simple tear-off label, which allows the garment to be easily rebranded. This is ideal for resellers looking to create their own brand.

With many customisation options available for colour and sizing, you can create your hoodie to your exact needs. This hoodie can be personalised with your own logo or design, with several options available for printing and embroidery. So, choose the AWDis college hoodie as the ideal choice for you and your group.

Features:

  • Huge range of colours makes this a really versatile choice
  • Durable and well-designed for a premium retail feel
  • Contains a tear-out label for easy re-branding
  • Double fabric hood with self-coloured cords
  • Front kangaroo pouch pocket
  • Ribbed cuffs and hem
  • Twin needle stitching detailing provides added strength and durability
  • Soft, cotton-faced fabric creates an ideal printing surface
  • Worldwide Responsible Accredited Production (WRAP) certified production
